parameters:
\N<Eliza>Pure Flame, I will support you!! I'll teach you the basics
of battle, it will be quick so listen well!!

\N<Pure Flame>Y-Yes!! But the enemy is already in front of us!! Please
hurry!!
チュートリアル_バトル_1

\N<Eliza>First, you can see the action order here!! The attacks will
start in the order listed on this chart!!

\N<Pure Flame>Yes!! So in this case, after my attack, it's the enemy's
turn to attack, right!!
\N<Eliza>Exactly!! Here it comes!! Try attacking now!!

\N<Eliza>For your first time, that was excellent!! Next, I'll teach
you the tricks of fighting!!
チュートリアル_バトル_2
\N<Eliza>You see the mark above the enemy's head, don't you?
\N<Pure Flame>Yes!! I see something like a rock-paper-scissors mark!!

\N<Eliza>Hmm!! That represents the opponent's battle style in an
easy-to-understand way. If you use a skill that can beat the
opponent's battle style, you can inhibit the enemy's
actions!!

\N<Pure Flame>Yes!! I understand!! I'll try to choose a skill that can win
at rock-paper-scissors!!

\N<Eliza>The rock-paper-scissors style assigned to skills changes
every time. It's not just about pushing through with strong
attacks, but also about dealing appropriately according to
the situation!!

About the Hold Attack: Some monsters, like the red enemies,
will launch a lewd attack known as the Hold Attack.

Normally, Pure Flame would not get caught, but after
witnessing "a certain event," she becomes susceptible to
getting caught by the Hold Attack.

name: 欲情洗脳された一般人
アルティメットブラックキュート
